desc: Bee Saving Paper is tree free paper made of lemongrass, designed to save exhausted bees. It contains sugar and honey plant seeds. Here you will find the products made of it like:wrapping paper, gift tags, notebook, art prints, bookmarks and greeting cards.

layout.text: Bee Saving Paper is tree free paper made of lemongrass. Thanks to its unique ingredients it works like an energy drink for exhausted bees.
